short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Adds a grid overlay to YouTube videos.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add a grid overlay with famous paintings as tile, the grid will be on the youtube video with cutouts to see through. You can change the number of tiles in the grid and toggle on or off the grid with buttons on the left.
